      correctAnswer: "workflows",
      explanation: "GitHub automatically detects workflow files placed in the .github/workflows/ directory of a repository. Any YAML file in this directory becomes a workflow that GitHub Actions can execute. The file name becomes the workflow's name in the GitHub UI."
