      question: "To count how many employees have entered their names in cells A2 through A100 (including text values), Priya should use the ________ function.",
      correctAnswer: "COUNTA",
      explanation: "COUNTA counts all non-empty cells, including those with text. COUNT only counts numeric cells. Since employee names are text, COUNTA is the correct choice to measure how many rows have been filled in."
