      explanation: "SQL execution order: FROM → WHERE → GROUP BY → HAVING → SELECT → ORDER BY. WHERE evaluates before groups are formed, so there's no AVG yet to compare. Use HAVING AVG(salary) > 70000 to filter after groups are formed."
